THE SINGLES COLLECTION tracks the work of the British pop singer after his work in the popular prog-rock band Genesis. This collection includes several of his biggest hits in music video and live form, including "Don't Lose My Number," "Sussudio," the love ballad "One More Night," and his be-boppy remake of "You Can't Hurry Love." Live versions of "Against All Odds" and "Who Said I Would" are unavailable anywhere else.
